fix: DEV-1324: DEV-1233: fix undo/redo for Audio (#440)

* fix: DEV-1324: fix undo/redo for Audio

- undo doesn't work for audio
  - if there was a draft, moved region will disappear after undo
  - if there was no drafts, nothing happens
- redo do nothing for audio (connected with previous)

* Create only one history step on region create

* Retry most failed test on fail (undo-redo)

* wait after drawing a polygon in e2e

* make pause before clicking on last point in e2e
